data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the serene and prestigious community of Quartz Hill! This exquisite 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence, built in 2004, boasts timeless elegance and modern comfort. With a recent and comprehensive remodel, this home is in impeccable condition, ready to welcome you and your family with open arms.    As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the attention to detail and high-quality craftsmanship that went into every aspect of this property. The interior is graced with an abundance of natural light, showcasing the thoughtful design and layout.    The spacious living areas are perfect for both relaxation and entertainment, offering a seamless flow from room to room. The heart of this home is the stunning gourmet kitchen, featuring top-of-the-line appliances, gleaming countertops, and an island that's ideal for culinary enthusiasts and gatherings with friends and family.    The five bedrooms provide ample space for a growing family, guests, or the flexibility to create your own private oasis. The bathrooms have been tastefully remodeled to offer modern convenience and style.    One of the standout features of this property is the meticulously maintained shutters that adorn every window, allowing you to control the natural light and privacy with ease.    Stepping outside, you'll find a beautifully landscaped yard that's perfect for outdoor relaxation and activities. Whether it's a morning coffee on the patio or a barbecue in the evening, you'll cherish your time spent in this serene outdoor space.    This home also enjoys a prime location, with a mansion community just across the road, adding to the exclusivity and charm of the neighborhood. Quartz Hill offers a peaceful and welcoming atmosphere, making it an ideal place to call home.    Don't miss your chance to own this stunning Quartz Hill residence. It's a rare opportunity to live in a completely remodeled, 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home built in 2004, in an excellent condition, surrounded by the beauty and tranquility of this exclusive neighborhood. Make this dream home yours and experience the epitome of gracious living in Quartz Hill. Schedule a showing today and prepare to be captivated by all this property has to offer!
